node.text:
[Fill A Pita] - Middle Eastern cuisine with 100% vegetarian & Halal ingredients. I had the following Pita Bread, Hummus, Labna Cheese, Fave Beans, Baklava, Falafels.
.

Order via WhatsApp 9299 9111
Aww man I miss eating out!
Fava beans! But they could be your fave too 😏
Nunca he visto al aguacate como algo que se deba calentar, igual con la lechuga 🤨🤔
